title: America's Test Kitchen Best Vegetable Recipes 33 Recipes from A
description:
[IMG]https://sanet.pics/storage-3/0817/6JKW3ZBdE9NuKsAkyHpLwrEkKp4kmnVt.jpg[/IMG]
America's Test Kitchen Best Vegetable Recipes: 33 Recipes from Artichokes to Zucchini(2017) - EPUB - zeke23
English | August 1, 2017 | ISBN: 1945256206, ASIN: B071NR4L2W | EPUB | 94 Pages | 77.3 MB
Roasted Artichokes (trim and drop in lemon water to prevent oxidizing, then toss in seasoned oil), Stir-Fried Asparagus with Shiitake Mushrooms (start in a hot pan and stir only occasionally for optimum char and caramelization), Broccoli with Lemon-Oregano Dressing (nuke it so it steams from the inside out), Quick Pickles (ready after 3 hours in the fridge), Braised Hearty Greens (our simple technique cuts out the parcooking step), Grilled Caesar Salad (a favorite salad meets fire, with better than you can imagine results); and, Twice-Baked Sweet Potatoes (adding an egg to the mashed flesh gives the potatoes structure and velvety smoothness)
